Package com.cinchapi.concourse.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FixedSizeIterableByteSequences
    A IterableByteSequences object where every sequence is the same size.
    IterableByteSequences
    A class should implement this interface if it wishes to return an iterator over an array of byte sequences where the number of sequences and the size of each sequence is variable.
